summary: If you like your dog but hate it every few seconds he let\'s out the exact same double bark? This mod is for you!
descriptionHtml:
Also avaible on SteamWorkshop: [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=14357]http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=14357[/url]

First of all sorry for my bad english!

If you like your dog but hate it every few seconds he let\'s out the exact same double bark? This mod is for you!

It simply removes the bark\'s sound from your game so it\'s compatible with all other mods because it doesn\'t modify any dogs in the game, it just removes this f*cking sound!

Installation:
Unzip and copy the \"shut up dogs.esp\" file into your Data folder.

Uninstall:
Delete \"shut up dogs.esp\".
author: pip99
